    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of aswritten’s brand language, from [finalized core taglines](narr:Position_TaglineFinalized) to the [iterative process](narr:Obs_TaglineIterationProcess) that balances trust and proof. The trajectory is marked by a shift from identity-based slogans toward use-case-driven positioning, most notably the [explicit supersession](narr:Position_TaglineSupersession) of the \"phone number\" metaphor in April. Recent work, such as the [July landing page draft](narr:Position_LandingPageTagline_Jul2026), continues to test how to anchor the product in specific conversations. The hub also archives the [Elephant Collective](narr:Narrative_ElephantCollective) \"dream bigger\" lineage, which serves as the foundational philosophy for narrative-as-weapon. Surrounding these core claims is a dense layer of [style observations](narr:StyleObs_2) that govern the brand's voice—including the use of [all-caps \"IS\" refrains](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis), [em-dash cadences](narr:StyleObs_EmDashRhetoric), and [antithetical framing](narr:StyleObs_SII_ThreeAxisAntithesis) to distinguish the product from AGI-centric competitors.""" ;
